paragraphs.text:
%elasticsearch
size 200
search /streaming-demo/logs {
     "sort": { "metadata.timestamp": { "order": "desc" }},
     "filter": {"and": [
         {"wildcard":{"metadata.zone":${Zone=Zone,*(Zone)|us-east1-b(us-east1-b)|us-east1-c(us-east1-c)|us-east1-d(us-east1-d)
         |us-central1-a(us-central1-a)|us-central1-(us-central1-b)|us-central1-c(us-central1-c)}}},
         {"wildcard":{"metadata.level":${Log Level=Log Level,*(Log Level)|trace(TRACE)|info(INFO)|error(ERROR)|fatal(FATAL)}}},
         {"range":{"metadata.timestamp":{"lte":${Time=Time,now-4h(Time)|now-5h(Last Hour)|
         now-16h(Last 12 Hours)|now-1d-4h(Last Day)|now-7d-4h(Last Week)}}}},
         {"wildcard":{"httpRequest.requestMethod":${Http Method=Http Method,*(Http Method)|get(GET)|put(PUT)|post(POST)|options(OPTIONS)|delete(DELETE)}}},
         {"term":{"httpResponse.status":${Response Status=Response Status,all(Response Status)|200(200)|201(201)|400(401)|500(500)}}},
          {"wildcard":{"appInfo.appId":"tapps"}}
    ]}}
